%H A079978 Clark Kimberling, <a href="https://cs.uwaterloo.ca/journals/JIS/VOL22/Kimberling/kimb9.html">A Combinatorial Classification of Triangle Centers on the Line at Infinity</a>, J. Int. Seq., Vol. 22 (2019), Article 19.5.4.
